title: Right In The Trend Basket 8/4: Yo-Semite, Beirut, Barack Obama, Fall Guys

description:
On this edition of Right in the Trend Basket Miles and DJ Danl discuss the President mispronouncing one of our National Parks, there was an enormous explosion in Beirut, it's Obama's birthday, and a new game from Devolver came out for free on PS+.
